                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7617" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0514</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2768 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人才护航方能“出海无忧”： 苏豪云商人才配备的困境探究</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Smooth Sailing” Requires Talent Support: Exploring the Challenges of Talent Allocation in  SOHO E-Commerce </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵宜萱，胡陈红，李璐，钱晋，赵曙明</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏苏豪云商有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">跨境电商；苏豪云商；人力资源管理；人才配备；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cross-border e-commerce; SOHO E-Commerce; Human Resource Management; Talent allocation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏苏豪云商有限公司(以下简称“苏豪云商”)成立于2021年，是省属企业中第一家实体跨境电商公司，目前正处于快速发展阶段。在数字经济背景下，苏豪云商致力于发挥人才核心竞争力，实现“成为江苏一流跨境电商引领者”的目标。本案例对苏豪云商人力资源管理进行梳理，发现其目前的人才配备与业务高速发展势头不匹配，存在人才“选-育-留”的问题。具体来说，新员工无法适应动态的岗位要求；中层管理者业务能力强，但管理能力欠佳；“老带新”的培训模式效果达不到预期，影响新业务推进；人才流失率低但员工缺乏活力。本案例试图通过对苏豪云商人力资源管理能力与业务发展需求不匹配的分析，启发案例使用者利用人力资源管理的相关理论分析、梳理并解决跨境电商企业快速发展过程中可能遇见的人才配备管理难题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Jiangsu SOHO E-Commerce Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as “SOHO E-Commerce”), the first entity cross-border e-commerce company among provincial enterprises in Jiangsu Province, was established in 2021 and is currently in a rapid development stage. In the context of the digital economy, SOHO E-Commerce is dedicated to leveraging its core talent competitiveness to achieve the goal of becoming a leading cross-border e-commerce company in Jiangsu province. This case study examines the human resource management of SOHO E-Commerce and identifies the mismatch between its talent allocation with talent “selection - training - retention” problems  and the fast-paced business growth. Specifically, new employees are unable to adapt to the dynamic job requirements; middle managers possess strong business skills, but lack sufficient managerial abilities; the “experienced mentoring new hires” training model does not yield the expected results, thus impacting the progress of new business initiatives; the employee turnover rate is low, but the staff lacks vitality. This case study aims to inspire users to utilize relevant theories of human resource management to analyze, streamline, and address talent allocation and management challenges that may arise during the rapid development of cross-border e-commerce enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《战略人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人才配备；员工招聘理论；管理者角色理论；人才梯队建设；人才培训与开发的方法和途径；自我决定理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
